 Customer Chat Plugin is a premium WordPress plugin that allows you to integrate yourMessenger experience directly into your website.

Customer Chat WordPress Plugin allows your customers to interact with your business anytime with the same personalized, rich-media experience they get onMessenger. Installation usually takes 2 minutes.

Customer Chat WordPress Plugin Features

[*]Improving your social media marketing strategy and subscribers` engagement.
[*]Getting your branding strategy in social media to a new level of awareness.
[*]Increasing the conversion rate and growing sales naturally.
[*]Providing a lightning-fast support for each customer by responses to their questions personally.
[*]Building a strong community by attracting new visitors and keeping your subscribers interested.
[*]Staying up-to-date and aware of users` wishes and demands while creating content or providing services
